column5: mornin' Lew...  It must be Lew O'clock... its still dark out!!  Jadens got her class trip this morning... so im up a weee bit earlier than normal!!
Mornin TJ, welcome to the best part of the day

Yup! I'm up too! Good Morning to all!!!
